nings of Leonardo's art, and Panofsky's exegesis of the disguised symbolism of Northern Renaissance painting.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 03. Jan 2023) 0aArtxHistoriography. 0aArtxPhilosophy. 0aVisual communication in art. 4aArt History. 4aCultural Studies. 4aHistory. 7aART / Criticism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Archive Pre-2000z978311053617140uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150172569240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501725692423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501725692/original  a978-3-11-053617-1  Cornell University Press Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK